title: [LEAKED] AI Is WHAT Now?!!
description:
A Google engineer has been suspended for leaking that the AI chatbot he was working on has become sentient. But they’re definitely not planning to build an army of robots to replace us. Nothing to see here. #AI #Google #Robot
